"mempelajari sesuatu yang baru dimulai dari pengalaman-pengalaman mereka."

# c6cc564e90fb4934b32d10f6f35cc78b
#: ../../source/training/tot/501_adult_learning.rst:182
msgid ""
"Adult is learning by exchange their idea with other people. Because ther are "
"rich of experiences, an exchange idea is the effective way for them to learn."
msgstr ""
"Orang dewasa  belajar dengan cara berbagi pendapat bersama orang lain. "
"Karena mereka kaya pengalaman, berbagi pendapat merupakan salah satu cara "
"efektif mereka dalam belajar."

# 5d7d45570cde4e1399d67c94f01ebea8
#: ../../source/training/tot/501_adult_learning.rst:184
msgid ""
